@ECHO OFF
REM DELTREE wildcard manual checks

MKDIR WTEST
MKDIR WTEST\SUB
MKSTAMP WTEST\KEEP.TXT keep
MKSTAMP WTEST\A.BAK bak1
MKSTAMP WTEST\B.BAK bak2
MKSTAMP WTEST\TMP.TMP tmp
MKSTAMP WTEST\SUB\NEST.TXT nested
ATTRIB +R WTEST\A.BAK

ECHO Removing WTEST\*.BAK ...
DELTREE /Y WTEST\*.BAK
IF EXIST WTEST\A.BAK ECHO FAIL: A.BAK still exists
IF EXIST WTEST\B.BAK ECHO FAIL: B.BAK still exists
IF NOT EXIST WTEST\KEEP.TXT ECHO FAIL: KEEP.TXT removed unexpectedly

ECHO Removing WTEST\???.TMP ...
DELTREE /Y WTEST\???.TMP
IF EXIST WTEST\TMP.TMP ECHO FAIL: TMP.TMP still exists

ECHO Removing all WTEST content via WTEST\* ...
DELTREE /Y WTEST\*
IF EXIST WTEST\KEEP.TXT ECHO FAIL: KEEP.TXT still exists
IF EXIST WTEST\SUB ECHO FAIL: SUB still exists

ECHO Removing empty WTEST root ...
DELTREE /Y WTEST
IF EXIST WTEST ECHO FAIL: WTEST still exists
